data.description: South Lakeland - As you enter the home, you are greeted by a warm and inviting living room complete with a cozy wood burning fireplace for relaxing on those cool nights. The living room flows seamlessly into the bonus/family room making it the perfect space to entertain guests. This home features a spacious layout with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms with an additional 4th bedroom/office. The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom with double vanities and a separate shower. Two additional bedrooms are perfect for guests and share a full bathroom with an additional 4th bedroom that can be used as an office. This home offers the seamless balance of work and play, whether you need a quiet space to work from home or a place to relax with family and friends, this home has it all.  Outside, you'll find a beautifully landscaped yard with plenty of room for outdoor activities or gardening. The home also features a two-car garage, providing ample parking and storage space and is situated on a quiet cul-de-sac.
